---
title: Southwestern Steak Tacos with SunGold Kiwi and Avocado Salsa
description: The color gold signifies riches, glitz, and extravagance—all apt adjectives to describe this dish. Its centerpiece is a salsa based around SunGold kiwis, which have sweet flesh in that opulent hue. But there are also some equally luxe accompaniments, like deeply spiced strips of beef and a nice dab of sour cream.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/southwestern-steak-tacos-ebba5d63.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/southwestern-steak-tacos-5462a916.pdf
servings: 2
author: HelloFresh
